  "name": "env_passthrough",
  "description": "Set HANDSHAKE_MT057=present in ProcessSpec.env; assert the process can read it via `printenv`. Exit_code == 0 only when the env var was actually injected; exit 7 marks 'env var missing'.",
  "spec": {
